[30;1m204 | [0m[35m~~~~~~~~~~~[0m
[30;1m205 | [0m[35m[0m

[30;1m207 | [0m[35mBecause ``asyncio`` is in general single-threaded, ``python-telegram-bot`` does currently not aim to[0m
